Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord2\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(407.167,180.389)}Hiruguerrilla of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord2\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(447.167,690.389)}Vampire Swamp
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if I'll catch one, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sucking my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a leech?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A leech?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's one on your\Nface, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, my blood-sucking leeches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn to\Nsuck their blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Return! Return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have my fill of\Ntheir healthy young blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:28.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hiruguerrilla's limbs function\Nlike blood-sucking leeches,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,allowing him to\Ndrink human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:41.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's a terrifying blood-sucking creature\Ncreated by Shocker headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A truly devilish invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Three children\Ngone missing," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days later,\Nand they still don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were all\Ntaken together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be a kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they went digging\Nfor crayfish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they\Nfell into the pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The police dredged the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but they couldn't\Nfind any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad\Nfeeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be certain yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the missing boys is the son\Nof a photography mentor of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I think about him,\NI just get so restless...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about my old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taken off every day since\Nthen from his photography job...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He insists he's going\Nto find Hisashi himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so he spends every\Nday searching...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisashi, where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Hiruguerrilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, and suck that man's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisashi, I know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're somewhere\Nnear this pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some kind of terrible\Nsecret in this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisashi.\NThat's what my gut tells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A leech?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Leeches, in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster... are you the\None who took the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll replace the blood\Nthat Hiruguerrilla drank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with this fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This will turn him\Ninto a mindless slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... to work, at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the experiment a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human whose blood is\Nreplaced with the green drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,adult or child,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,will be reduced to the intelligence\Nof a primitive ape-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They will serve Shocker's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been back\Nsince last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you told the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They investigated at once,\Nbut they couldn't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They did find this in the\Ngrass near the pond, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that his?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's halfway through\Nthe film roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's develop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an78\bord5}Dark Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Shocker was behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to that\Npond than meets the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Too quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's\Nsomething lurking nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato and Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to force you\Nto fight separately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker monsters...\NWe'll settle this another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:33.06,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting Kamen Rider track us here\Nwas a foolish mistake, Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will move on to Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the man you should thank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki's all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading over\Nto see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you were lonely\Nwithout your husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so the Chairman and Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But won't that be more trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Leeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to suck your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All of your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A leech!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this drug myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When one of our\Nslaves drinks this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they will return to\Ntheir old selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hiruguerrilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a cyborg I went to\Ngreat lengths to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisashi! Eiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad to see, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you want to see\Nthem restored to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please,\Nturn them back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything you want!\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?\NIs that you, Mr. Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm underneath\Nthe vampire swamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,taken hostage in Shocker's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They have Eiko and Hisashi\Nas well as Yuri and Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, there's a cave\Non the edge of the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come in that\Nway, you won't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll come save you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,Just hang in there until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take him to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiruguerrilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato will be\Ncoming here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink his blood before he\Ncan become the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I won't be\Nwalking into your trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew there was something\Nto this place from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been turned into slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.\NWhat an awful thing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The medicine to restore them\Nis in the room down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamazaki...\Nleave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one more step, Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I press this switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the bottom will come\Nout of the swamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the water will fill\Nthis place instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The slaves will all drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, Hiruguerrilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I shall turn\Nyou into our slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this medicine to Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On your feet, slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At last,\NIchimonji Hayato is my slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone, insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you want to end\Nup like Ichimonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, my slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be excellent to watch\Nyou take each other out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I need to push the\Nlever to drain the swamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Go save the\Npeople in the cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Face me, Hiruguerrilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy him, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape\Nme, Hiruguerrilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:27.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider can unleash his power\Nas a tremendous electrical charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The medicine restored\Nthem all to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hip-hip hooray! Hip-hip hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:01.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrible monster\NHiruguerrilla was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:04.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But where would Doctor\NDeath head next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:08.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And what is the next monster that\NIchimonji Hayato would have to face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.72,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:14.26,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:15.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Isoginchack!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He attacks Kamen Rider with 100\Nmeter-per-second wind speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The tornadoes generated\Nfrom Isoginchack's mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:25.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,engulf one person after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:31.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Man-Eating\NMonster Isoginchack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(457.167,725.389)}The Man-Eating\NMonster Isoginchack
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:41.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:43.64,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.64,0:23:45.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:51.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:52.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.69,0:23:56.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:58.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:04.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:07.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:11.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:15.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiruguerrilla of\Nthe Vampire Swamp